Name: txw2
Version: 20110809
Release: alt2_18jpp8
Summary: Typed XML writer for Java
License: CDDL-1.1 and GPLv2 with exceptions
URL: https://txw.dev.java.net

# svn export https://svn.java.net/svn/jaxb~version2/tags/txw2-project-20110809/ txw2-20110809
